  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Then I separated twelve of the chief of the priests,.... That were in company with him; so that it seems there were more than the two mentioned, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 8:2",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", very probably their families, or some of their brethren, were with them: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Sherebiah, Hashabiah, and ten of their brethren with them; these men named were Levites, and not priests, Ezra 8:18 and therefore the copulative \"and\" must be supplied: ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Sherebiah, Hashabiah, and ten of their brethren with them; these men named were Levites, and not priests, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Ezra 8:18",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " and therefore the copulative \"and\" must be supplied: ",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and Sherebiah, &c. or with the twelve priests, Sherebiah, &c. and ten Levites more with them; so that the number of priests and Levites were equal, and in all twenty four. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and Sherebiah, &c. or with the twelve priests, Sherebiah, &c. and ten Levites more with them; so that the number of priests and Levites were equal, and in all twenty four. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
